citeinfo.title:
Diets of Nestling Tufted Puffins (
Fratercula cirrhata
) in the Gulf of Alaska and Eastern Aleutian Islands in 1986, with Special Reference to "Forage Fish"

abstract.p:
This report describes field work and preliminary results of a study of the diets of nestling tufted puffins (
Fratercula cirrhata
) at several breeding colonies in the northern and western Gulf of Alaska between Prince William Sound and Unimak Pass during late summer 1986.
